										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Once in a while I&#8217;d come across a screenshot of a cool UI that I think would be relatively simple to recreate in Figma, so I made it a personal challenge to do so. This is not something that I do in my spare time or anything because, quite frankly I don&#8217;t have any spare time anymore. This is more of a distraction to prevent me from going insane between juggling 3 different major projects atm.</p>
